{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/ciayo-comics-comiconnect-tour-2018-ajang-kumpul-dan-berbagi-ilmu-para-kreator-komik/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"CIAYO Comics ComiConnect Tour 2018, Ajang Kumpul dan Berbagi Ilmu Para Kreator Komik","content":"<h4 style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>Press Release</strong></h4>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>CIAYO Comics adalah sebuah platform komik digital yang berisi komik-komik lokal super keren buatan komikus Indonesia dengan berbagai genre, mulai dari action, drama, romance, horror, thriller dan comedy.</em></p>\n<p>Jakarta, 14 Maret 2018 &#8211; Platform komik digital asal Indonesia,<a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"> CIAYO Comics</a> sukses mengadakan seminar bertajuk <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/comiconnect-tour-2018-bakal-datang-ke-kotamu/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">CIAYO Comics <em>ComiConnect Tour 2018</em></a><strong>.</strong> Acara yang diadakan di  Lo.Ka.Si, Bandung, 10 Maret 2018 ini dihadiri Lebih dari 130 peserta  yang merupakan kreator-kreator komik lokal yang juga didukung oleh komunitas komik lokal di Bandung.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45118\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45118\" data-attachment-id=\"45118\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ciayo-comics-comiconnect-tour-2018-ajang-kumpul-dan-berbagi-ilmu-para-kreator-komik/attachment/cct11/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/cct11.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;2.8&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;ILCE-7S&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1520688341&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;35&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;1250&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.005&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: CIAYO Comics&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/cct11-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/cct11.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-45118 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/cct11.jpg\" alt=\"Peserta ComiConnect Tour 2018 di Bandung. ComiConnect akan mengunjungi 11 kota besar di sepanjang tahun 2018. (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/cct11.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/cct11-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45118\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Peserta ComiConnect Tour 2018 di Bandung. ComiConnect akan mengunjungi 11 kota besar di sepanjang tahun 2018. (Sumber: Pictures)</p></div></p>\n<p>Untuk mengisi seminar ini, <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">CIAYO Comics</a> menghadirkan <em>scripwriter</em> komik digital <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/heartbeat\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Hearbeat</a>, Tessa YP dan komikus kondang Bandung, Sweta Kartika. Sesi pertama dibawakan oleh Tessa YP yang berbagi informasi tentang detail cara membuat karakter protagonis dan antagonis yang menarik. Dilanjutkan oleh Sweta Kartika yang membahas tentang cara menggambar anatomi dan <em>gesture</em> di komik.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45113\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45113\" data-attachment-id=\"45113\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ciayo-comics-comiconnect-tour-2018-ajang-kumpul-dan-berbagi-ilmu-para-kreator-komik/attachment/cct6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/cct6.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;2.8&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;ILCE-7S&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1520688341&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;35&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;1250&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.005&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sweta Kartika memberikan materi kepada kreator yang hadir. (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sweta Kartika memberikan materi kepada kreator yang hadir. (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/cct6-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/cct6.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45113\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/cct6.jpg\" alt=\"Sweta Kartika memberikan materi kepada kreator yang hadir. (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/cct6.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/cct6-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45113\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sweta Kartika memberikan materi kepada kreator yang hadir. (Sumber: CIAYO Pictures)</p></div></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45115\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45115\" data-attachment-id=\"45115\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ciayo-comics-comiconnect-tour-2018-ajang-kumpul-dan-berbagi-ilmu-para-kreator-komik/attachment/cct8/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/cct8.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;2.8&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;ILCE-7S&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1520688341&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;35&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;1250&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.005&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Tessa YP memberikan materi script writing kepada kreator yang hadir. (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Tessa YP memberikan materi script writing kepada kreator yang hadir. (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/cct8-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/cct8.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45115\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/cct8.jpg\" alt=\"Tessa YP memberikan materi script writing kepada kreator yang hadir. (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/cct8.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/cct8-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45115\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tessa YP memberikan materi <em>script writing</em> kepada kreator yang hadir. (Sumber: CIAYO Pictures)</p></div></p>\n<p>Cerita dan ilustrasi memang menjadi kunci utama dalam menciptakan komik yang mempunyai nilai jual yang tinggi. Itu juga yang ingin <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">CIAYO Comics</a> sampaikan kepada para kreator di seluruh Indonesia. CEO <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/ciayocorp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">CIAYO Corp</a>, Borton Liew, pada saat menyampaikan sambutannya dalam acara ini menegaskan pentingnya IP bagi para kreator, “<em>Intelectual Property</em> (IP) itu sangat perlu dikembangkan dan di monitor. Karena dari sebuah IP itu kita bisa membuat banyak produk turunan yang menjual. Bahkan komik sendiri itu salah satu turunan IP” ungkapnya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45114\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45114\" data-attachment-id=\"45114\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ciayo-comics-comiconnect-tour-2018-ajang-kumpul-dan-berbagi-ilmu-para-kreator-komik/attachment/cct7/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/cct7.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;2.8&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;ILCE-7S&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1520688341&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;35&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;1250&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.005&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Borton Liew, CEO CIAYO Comics menjelaskan pentingnya managemenrt Intelectual Property terhadap industri komik Indonesia. (Sumber: CIAYO Pictures)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Borton Liew, CEO CIAYO Comics menjelaskan pentingnya managemenrt Intelectual Property terhadap industri komik Indonesia. (Sumber: CIAYO Pictures)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/cct7-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/cct7.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45114\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/cct7.jpg\" alt=\"Borton Liew, CEO CIAYO Comics menjelaskan pentingnya managemenrt Intelectual Property terhadap industri komik Indonesia. (Sumber: CIAYO Pictures)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/cct7.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/cct7-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45114\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Borton Liew, CEO CIAYO Comics menjelaskan pentingnya managemenrt Intelectual Property terhadap industri komik Indonesia. (Sumber: CIAYO Pictures)</p></div></p>\n<p>Tujuan utama diadakan <strong>CIAYO <em>Comics Connect</em></strong> ini juga untuk memperkenalkan program <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">CIAYO Comics</a> yang baru, <strong>CIAYO <em>Class</em></strong>. Program ini diperuntukan bagi para kreator yang komiknya berpotensi tetapi masih perlu diasah lagi untuk bisa menjadi komik yang menjual. Nantinya, komik-komik dalam program ini akan mendapat masukan dari tim editorial di CIAYO Comics selama tiga bulan sampai layak menjadi komik <em>official</em> di CIAYO Comics. Selain itu CIAYO Comics juga mengumumkan <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ciayo-comics-challenge-vol-3-total-hadiahnya-450-juta-rupiah/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">CIAYO Comics Challenge Vol.3 dengan hadiah total 450 juta rupiah.</a></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45116\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45116\" data-attachment-id=\"45116\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ciayo-comics-comiconnect-tour-2018-ajang-kumpul-dan-berbagi-ilmu-para-kreator-komik/attachment/cct9/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/cct9.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;2.8&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;ILCE-7S&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1520688341&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;35&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;1250&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.005&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Beny Maulana (kiri) menjelaskan tentang program CIAYO Class dan CIAYO Comics Challenge vol.3. (Sumber: CIAYO Pictures)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt; Beny Maulana (kiri) menjelaskan tentang program CIAYO Class dan CIAYO Comics Challenge vol.3. (Sumber: CIAYO Pictures)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/cct9-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/cct9.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45116\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/cct9.jpg\" alt=\" Beny Maulana (kiri) menjelaskan tentang program CIAYO Class dan CIAYO Comics Challenge vol.3. (Sumber: CIAYO Pictures)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/cct9.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/cct9-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45116\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Beny Maulana (kiri) menjelaskan tentang program CIAYO Class dan CIAYO Comics Challenge vol.3. (Sumber: CIAYO Pictures)</p></div></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/comiconnect-tour-2018-bakal-datang-ke-kotamu/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">CIAYO Comics ComiConnect Tour 2018</a> bukan hanya ada di Bandung tapi juga akan mengunjungi 10 kota terpilih di seluruh Indonesia. Kota yang berpotensi memiliki banyak komikus muda berbakat ini diseleksi langsung oleh tim CIAYO Comics. Bandung sebagai pembuka CIAYO Comics ComiConnect Tour 2018 akan disusul oleh Yogyakarta, Makassar, Surabaya, Semarang, Bali, Medan, Aceh, Batam, Tegal dan akan di tutup di CIAYO Comics HQ Jakarta.</p>\n<p>Informasi lebih lanjut hubungi:</p>\n<p>Michael Tan</p>\n<p>Public Relation CIAYO Corp</p>\n<p><a href=\"mailto:Michael.tanajo@gmail.com\">Michael.tanajo@gmail.com</a></p>\n<p>+6282273170103</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"57d5de57-70d2-5833-9ed3-a72f7af19baf"}}}